Complete the solution so that it reverses the string passed into it.
'world'  =>  'dlrow'


My Code
function solution(str){
  const arr = [];
  for (let i = 0; i < str.length; i++){
    arr.push(str[i]);
  }
  arr.reverse();
  const result = arr.join("")
  return result;
}


Other Code
function solution(str){
  return str.split('').reverse().join('');  
}

split으로 한글자씩 나누고 join으로 다시 합침